Pressotel beta fisting
Step 1: String Input -> nextLine()
Step 2: Convert the String into String Array using split() function
Step 3: Create a ans String empty
Step 4: Iterate using for loop -> String Array
Step 5: Set the condition whether your ans string length is
lesser than string word length() if true
assign ans to that word
Step 6: After for loop print your ans*/

